        <p>Miller, G.T. (2002). Living in the environment. 12th ed. California: A Division of Wadsworth.</p>
        <p>White, I.D., Mottershead, D.N., and Harrison, S.J. (1996). Environmental system: An Introductory Text. Second Edition., London: Chapman & Hall.</p><br><br>
